#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
typedef long long ll;
int main()
{
    ll t;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
        ll n,k,a,s=0;
        cin>>n>>k;
        for(ll i=0;i<n;i++){
        cin>>a;
        s+=a;
        }
        if((s<k)||(s==k))
            cout<<"Yes"<<endl;
        else
            cout<<"No"<<endl;

    }
}
